data.description: Beautiful Contemporary style POOL home & perfect for today's families!  Flexible floorplan to accommodate various family needs  This fabulous home is in the Preserve at Lake Thomas in Land O Lakes & close to everything!  Sitting at the entrance of the community with its own PRIVATE GATE.  Beautiful homesite sitting on a small fishing lake with a PRIVATE DOCK.  Detailed elevation with 3 car spacious garage.  Formal living & dining room included with this home & perfect to showcase it.  Tuck behind the formal areas are the leisure & morning rooms overlooking the pool & rear yard.  Sizeable kitchen with a large serving and/or preparing island.  Updated STAINLESS STEEL appliances & sink overlooking the gorgeous rear view.  Generous size laundry room with soaking tub.  Full POOL bath included with direct access to the lanai area.  First floor den with double entry doors.  Equally impressive 2nd floor with a huge master suite & included en suite.  Walk-in closets.  Flex space adjacent the room, currently set up as a bedroom but could easily be a secondary den, large walk-in closet, gaming area, media room, etc.  2 secondary bedrooms with a spacious shared bath.  Hall linen closet.  Guest wing with PRIVATE BATH, & walk-in closet.  Recently resurfaced lanai space with screen-in pool.  Screen is upgraded to reduce sunburns.  Carpet is upgraded to be water resistant.  No carpet on the first floor!  Come & start your new chapter with this lovely home!
